v0.45.1 (October 01, 2025)
--------------------------

The is a patch release to fix an issue with `Windows wheels <https://github.com/numba/llvmlite/issues/1297>`_.

Pull-Requests:

* PR `#1307 <https://github.com/numba/llvmlite/pull/1307>`_: GHA/win-64 add delvewheel repair to bundle ``msvcp140.dll`` (`swap357 <https://github.com/swap357>`_)
* PR `#1310 <https://github.com/numba/llvmlite/pull/1310>`_: Change-log 0.45.1 (`esc <https://github.com/esc>`_)

Authors:

* `esc <https://github.com/esc>`_
